metadata.name: Contemplative Monkey Officer
metadata.description: This work should have just been an experiment involving DSLR, Ray Tracing and golden ratio combinations. But the monkey's gaze has become something so real, human and perfect that it forces me not to dismiss it as a mere experimental exercise. I just loved this monkey from the first moment I saw those beautiful, sincere eyes. This monkey convinced me to improve these techniques and soon I will bring you more items about this monkey civilization.
